ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"又返炒"},{"pid":"6accdc41f774651d2e1d981481a766b3a927f301","tid":990162,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"白光其實係光譜上所有色頻推到最大<br />\n你開個小畫家出嚟揀調色盤<br />\nRed 255<br />\nGreen 255<br />\nBlue 255<br />\n就係白色<br />\n相反，將所有紅綠藍色推到零<br />\n就係黑色<br />\n<br />\n你肉眼可以睇到各樣物件<br />\n一係件物件本身發光<br />\n光譜嘅總和就係白色<br />\n一係外在光線射落去再反射入你隻眼<br />\n物件嘅顏色其實就係入射收到嘅光譜減去物料吸收咗嘅光譜<br />\n例如蘋果係紅色因為佢吸收咗紅色以外光<br />\n你見到件黑衫因為佢吸收哂所有光<br />\n無光反射出嚟嘅結果<br />\n之所以黑色衫吸熱<br />\n白色衫耀眼唔吸熱就係因為佢反射哂啲光出嚟"},{"pid":"bf5143710798b1c0ad68f8dfff12e9ac288b08f1","tid":990162,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"自己望下黑色喺黑譜邊度"},{"pid":"f6d4bbfb0647832d1bd43b45b066b15d34eee3cb","tid":990162,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5143710798b1c0ad68f8dfff12e9ac288b08f1","tid":990162,"uid":223818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"自己望下黑色喺黑譜邊度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"光譜"},{"pid":"b67aeddcec603afaf78bbdf88e7422ecf6432a5a","tid":990162,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"問陶喆"},{"pid":"5fdbedf67c1078f8c22214b7efa4d70952e5e5bc","tid":990162,"uid":144660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"907b7e2199881dd0a3169bfafd1f7ced6a867233","tid":990162,"uid":7837,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T11:33:38.000Z","msg":"睇左做黑色嘅橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"睇完回覆先知原來係講燈 唔係橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b86d2a32e57e04983e2e7f2f30b32447e3d592","tid":990162,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1c8b6a3b280bcc3110432fa6811787caeedea20","tid":990162,"uid":52972,"like"